commit.message:
(DImode patterns): Add `&' to target operand constraints.

From-SVN: r2594

files.patch:
@@ -30,7 +30,7 @@
 ;; Addition insns.
 
 (define_insn "adddi3"
-  [(set (match_operand:DI 0 "di_operand" "=r")
+  [(set (match_operand:DI 0 "di_operand" "=&r")
 	(plus:DI (match_operand:DI 1 "di_operand" "%r")
 		 (match_operand:DI 2 "di_operand" "r")))]
   ""

 ")

 		  (match_operand:DI 2 "di_operand" "r")))]
   ""
